{
  "stem": "523.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told that me and my brother won't take long, and we will die too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he didn't suppose to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the way he treated us, it was understandable what-- what he meant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he took right away over our parents, every our belongings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because whatever my parents had, they didn't had a chance even to exchange it because they die right away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe they would survive that first winter, because this first winter, '42-- people-- the most of the people will die was in this winter, because it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people were dropping dead right and left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my parents even didn't had even a chance to exchange anything from their belonging-- maybe something, but that's about all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he took over all our parents' belongings and thought that it won't take long, we will be dead too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But miracles, we both survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh yeah, there were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But people-- everybody was thinking for themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People-- when you keep people like animals, eventually that will they become.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were thinking for themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People buried their own children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Children buried their parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not a normal life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People didn't think about others.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People think how to survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What the meaning to survival doesn't making any difference, just to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So this was the first winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After I went through this, I was sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My-- I had frostbites.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was filled with sores.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was in such bad shape that it's a miracle how I survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After the first winter, my brother went to work in the factory where they make furniture just to work a-- The Ukrainian people got paid for it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the Jewish people who worked there worked for little pieces of wood or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
